---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms and Conditions"
  description="Terms and conditions for McIvor Power Vac duct cleaning services in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-primary-900 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-300">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
          Welcome to McIvor Power Vac. By using our duct cleaning and related services, you agree to the following terms and conditions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          McIvor Power Vac provides professional air duct cleaning, dryer vent cleaning, and insulation removal services for residential and commercial properties in Saskatoon and surrounding areas.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          All services are subject to scheduling availability and site conditions. We reserve the right to decline service if conditions are unsafe or unsuitable for our equipment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Scheduling and Access</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          To perform our services, we require:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Access to your furnace, air handler, and all duct registers</li>
          <li>Clear working space around the furnace (minimum 3 feet)</li>
          <li>Someone present (18 years or older) during the service</li>
          <li>Pets secured in a separate area during service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Pricing and Payment</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Quotes are provided based on information you supply about your property. Final pricing may be adjusted if actual conditions differ significantly from what was described.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Payment is due upon completion of service unless other arrangements have been made in advance. We accept cash, cheque, and major credit cards.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We understand plans change. Please provide at least 24 hours notice if you need to reschedule or cancel your appointment. Late cancellations or no-shows may be subject to a service fee.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Service Limitations</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Our duct cleaning service includes cleaning of accessible ductwork, registers, and furnace components. Some limitations apply:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>We cannot clean ducts that are inaccessible, damaged, or contain asbestos</li>
          <li>Pre-existing damage to ductwork is not our responsibility</li>
          <li>We do not perform HVAC repairs (we can recommend qualified technicians)</li>
          <li>Results may vary based on the condition and age of your duct system</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          McIvor Power Vac carries liability insurance for our services. We take care to protect your property, but we are not responsible for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Pre-existing conditions or damage</li>
          <li>Damage resulting from defective ductwork or equipment</li>
          <li>Consequential damages or loss of use</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Satisfaction</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We take pride in our thorough work. If you have any concerns about the service provided, please contact us within 7 days so we can address the issue.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          If you have questions about these terms, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {siteConfig.contact.phone}</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> {siteConfig.contact.email}</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> {siteConfig.contact.address.street}, {siteConfig.contact.address.city}, {siteConfig.contact.address.state} {siteConfig.contact.address.zip}</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
